---
title: Coconut Chilli Chicken with Stir Fried Mushroom Jasmine Rice
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Coconut Chicken with Mushrooms in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coconut-chilli-chicken-34bfc323-b8b29d6d.jpg
